name: Surely we will starve
description: *Housewives twirl* "Okay Pookie, I'm all ready to go! I was thinking I might like to have Thai, but I know you don't care for that spicy food. Maybe the steakhouse? No...every time we go there you're up all night scratching. I know! How about Olive Garden? You do love their breadsticks!" "Oh for the love of Dog Edith! Wouldja just pick someplace already I'm starving!" Paper collage + digital collage
